@host = http://localhost:8080/api/v1
@token = Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### Submit Feedback
POST {{host}}/feedbacks
Authorization: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "subject": "App Feedback",
  "message": "Great application!",
  "rating": 5
}

### Submit Feedback (Edge Case - Missing Rating)
POST {{host}}/feedbacks
Authorization: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "subject": "No Rating"
}

### Get My Feedbacks
GET {{host}}/feedbacks/me
Authorization: {{token}}

### Get All Feedbacks (Admin)
GET {{host}}/admin/feedbacks
Authorization: {{token}}

### Reply to Feedback (Admin)
POST {{host}}/admin/feedbacks/1/reply
Authorization: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "adminReply": "Thank you for the feedback!"
}
